data.name: FailReason
desc: These values specify the reason why a type conversion failed.

items.name: OUT_OF_RANGE
lines: The given value does not fit in the range of the destination type.

items.name: IS_NOT_NUMBER
lines: The given value cannot be converted to a number.

items.name: IS_NOT_ENUM
lines: The given value cannot be converted to an enumeration.

items.name: IS_NOT_BOOL
lines: The given value cannot be converted to a boolean.

items.name: NO_SUCH_INTERFACE
lines: The given value is not an interface or cannot queried to the right interface.

items.name: SOURCE_IS_NO_DERIVED_TYPE
lines: The given value cannot be converted to right structure or exception type.

items.name: TYPE_NOT_SUPPORTED
lines: The type class of the given value is not supported.

items.name: INVALID
lines: The given value cannot be converted and none of the other reasons match.
